questions.quote: Okay listen, y'know when you move in Rachel's room is gonna be empty, you wanna talk about what we want to do with it?
God! I can't believe she saved me for last. Why are they taking so long?
I don't know, I mean you were a lot bigger, I mean, stronger back then.
Well, from me. And I know it's not your big money song, but it's my favorite.
Yeah, I'll be fine. But could someone please make sure that sandwich is gone when I get out there?
No that's what you do when you want to get the truth out of someone.
Look, I just think you're an adult, okay? And you should get over your silly fears.
All right! But uh, listen, what do you say we crank it up a notch?
Kind of. She's coming by to interview us and see where we live.
Oooh, did he put a little starch in your bloomers? Who said that?
